<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="21Nov1931"><font color="red">21 November 1931</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I [want to know when you expect to have access] to the MS of <i>W.i.P.</i> &hellip; I got Lucia (by a ruse) to make me elaborate capitals for the poems &hellip; Faber and Faber who were to have sent me a large type proof sent me on Nov. 20 &hellip; a proof pulled on Oct 16 which is identical with the proof pulled on 21 Sept. &hellip; I am stitching away like a cobbler </div>
